snippet.title: Obama Alien Defense FULL Walkthrough *HD*
snippet.description:
Video Summary: I'll be Obama and I will kill aliens?!

Description: Obama vs Aliens; Obama must fight through groups of aliens until all of them have been eradicated from New York and London. Obama must fight small aliens, medium aliens and big bosses including mother ships to kill the breed of creatures. He will have the ability to pick up plasma guns and other weapons to kill the aliens. The only problem with this game is that if you die once you lose all your presidential coins. Enjoy!

Play the Game: http://www.miniclip.com/games/obama-alien-defense/en/

Please Subscribe, Like or Comment!
